Shared code/file for the ROSACE use case

This part of the code is "shared" by the various implementation
namelly, POSIX, XtratuM, RTEMS and TASTE (generated from AADL specs).

A Makefile allows users to compute WCET for all functions, to be used
with Bound-T for SPARC LEON3 processors. wcet.txt provides reference
output, unit is number of instructions cycles.
